VersionSystem
=============

Provides versioning every time a git-commit is performed.


Example
=======

To use within your app:

	<span class="release">
		Release: <%= "#{APP_VERSION.year}.#{APP_VERSION.revision}" %>, Released on: <%= APP_VERSION.rel_date.strftime("%d %B %Y, %I:%M:%S") %>
	</span>


